{"tid":1485752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝和理非，多謝勇武","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:05.000Z","uid":162971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7edee1478e7be4c219a1090b251c4958e4d346","tid":1485752,"uid":162971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"今日和理非，以人數同行動話畀勇武，話畀政府聽<br />\n<br />\n經過兩個月嘅抗爭，和理非並無割𥱊！<br />\n<br />\n而勇武亦都尊重和理非，一齊和平一次，表現出可<br />\n<br />\n進可退之勇<br />\n<br />\n雖然出邊好多post屌緊金鐘留守手足遲遲都唔走，<br />\n<br />\n有部分一撚定係分化，有部分一定真心為手足好，<br />\n<br />\n雖然語氣不完美，但可接受，亦有待改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之都係嗰句，核彈都唔撚割！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">可檢討！不分化！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港  時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b2c840990a80a1c5223388eaddcd846f0a38cdbb","tid":1485752,"uid":266683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSpuTek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSpuTek.jpg&h=be824e3d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}